      "title": "WARGEAR ABILITIES",
      "entries": [
        {
          "type": "statement",
          "text": "Once per battle for each Aspect Shrine token this unit has, you can change the result of one Hit roll or one Wound roll made for a model in this unit (excluding CHARACTER models) to an unmodified 6.",
